<h2 class="bold font-l">Anakin sees the future</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Star Wars: The Clone Wars; in the final episode of the Mortis arc, the Son (the physical embodiment of the Dark Side) shows Anakin his future, that he will fall to the Dark Side, betray the Jedi and become Darth Vader. Anakin accepts the Son's offer of an alliance to stop the visions from coming true and turns to the Dark Side until the Father wipes the visions from his mind. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
